### Privacy Policy for the Simple CVSS 3.1 Calculator Chrome Extension
Introduction
Thank you for choosing to use our Chrome extension. Your privacy is important to us and we are committed to protecting it. This privacy policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and what rights you have. Please read it carefully.

### What Information We Collect
Our Chrome extension does not collect any personal information. We do not collect, store, use, or share any information about users who install and use our extension.

### How We Use Information
Since our extension does not collect any personal information, we do not use or share any information.

### Your Rights
If you have questions about our privacy policy, you can contact us at the provided email address. Since we do not collect any personal information, we cannot identify you or access your personal information.

### Changes to Our Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to make changes to our privacy policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page.
